Teen Anal Nightmares 2 is a noteworthy addition to the creampie genre. Like the inestimable masterpiece, Dirt Pipe Milkshakes 2, before it, Anal Nightmares 2 explores the inner cavities of Man's psychosexual nature, presenting to its viewer a nuanced interpretation of the inherent conflicts between Man's id, ego, and superego. Both deliver to their audiences an inspiring story of a protagonist's analeptic journey through the bowels of corruption toward the salvation of moral rectitude. However, whereas the plot and dialogue of Dirt Pipe Milkshakes 2 fully conceptualizes and develops its characters - particularly its two protagonists, Wesley Pipes and Kyla Coxxx - and constructs a complex, diagetic world about them, Anal Nightmares falls well short in these regards. The latter's characters are flaccid and banal; its world, a morass of cliched metaphors. Anal Nightmares immediately arouses its audience, capturing their attention with an unrelenting cinematic grip. For the first ten minutes of the film, the audience's passion is stroked as the plot builds toward a premature crescendo. Unfortunately, that herky-jerky ride abrubtly comes to an end, just ten minutes into the film, and Anal Nightmares becomes a dull, pointless, sleep-inducing traipse of ass-fucking. Alas, such short-comings afflict most works in the annals of creampie cinema, even those in the highly-regarded Dirt Pipe Milkshakes oeuvre.
